title: The Opie and Anthony Podcast Episodes 1-51 many episodes missing
description:
Audio
Format .mp3
Bit rate 128 Kbps

An ill-fated attempt to recompile the first 51 episodes of The Opie & Anthony Podcast. These episodes are no longer available through typical mediums and I have had a surprisingly difficult time tracking them down. All of these episodes were downloaded from YouTube and converted to .mp3 using XMedia Recode.

I have not personally listened to most of these files and apologize in advance for any errors. I am still trying to locate missing episodes and will upload a complete collection of first 51 episodes when they are found. Any help tracking down missing episodes, or nudge in the right direction, is much appreciated.

I thoroughly enjoyed listening to these podcasts when they were available and have been kicking myself for not downloading them when I had the chance. If you are not familiar with O&A or the O&A Podcast, I would personally recommend starting out with Episode #36 Jim Norton Hates Animals, too funny.

Enjoy!
